g++ JavaNativeHelloWorld.cpp -I/opt/ibm/jdk60sr10/include -shared -m32 -o libhelloworld.so
/opt/ibm/jdk60sr10/bin/javac JavaNativeHelloWorld.java



On IBM i for JDK 6064 compressedrefs:(In fact, the .so file is also works for default JDK 60 64bit.). It's built on chaos. AIX 5.3.

xlC_r -O3 -DIPv6_FUNCTION_SUPPORT -q64 -q mbcs -qlanglvl=extended -qarch=ppc -qinfo=pro -qalias=noansi -qxflag=LTOL:LTOL0 -qsuppress=1506-1108 -D_XOPEN_SOURCE_EXTENDED=1 -D_ALL_SOURCE -DRS6000 -DAIXPPC -D_LARGE_FILES -DPPC64 -g -qtbtable=full -qlist -qsource -DJ9OS_I5 -qhalt=w -I. -I/afs/rchland.ibm.com/lande/shadow/dev2000/osxpf/v6r1m0f.xj9/bld/shadow/pase.pgm/j9.xj9/jdk60/64bit26/jre/lib/ppc64/compressedrefs/include -qtbtable=full -qlist -qsource -c -o JavaNativeHelloWorld.o JavaNativeHelloWorld.cpp 
   
ld -b64 -G -bnoentry -bernotok -bE:JavaNativeHelloWorld.exp -L. -o libhelloworld.so JavaNativeHelloWorld.o -lc_r -lC_r -lm -lpthread 
